original_title: Number of dengue related deaths in Sri Lanka up to 38
original_body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); The number of dengue related deaths reported in Sri Lanka has increased to 38.
1,149 dengue cases have been reported during the first week of August.
The highest number of patients, 28,746, were reported from the Western Province.
